# 忽略所有文件
*

# 允许文件夹结构
!*/

# 只允许 cpp 和 h 文件
!*.cpp
!*.h

# 如果需要保留 CMakeLists.txt (通常建议保留)
!**/CMakeLists.txt

# 明确排除所有 build 文件夹和压缩包
.vs/
.qtcreator/
build/
out/
icons/
*.ui
*.qrc

!*.cxx

# 4. 允许 vrbindings 文件夹及其内容
!**/vrbindings/
!**/vrbindings/*

!**/CMakeLists.txt
!README.md

# Allow Doxygen documentation source and GitHub Actions workflow files.
!**/Doxyfile
!**/doxygen/
!**/doxygen/**
!**/.github/
!**/.github/**
!**/.gitignore
